                <h1>Personalize Your iPhone: Change Your Wallpaper Easily</h1>
                <p>Changing the background on your iPhone is a simple yet effective way to personalize your device. To do this, go to Settings, select Wallpaper, and choose a new image from your library or Apple's collection. You can set it as the lock screen, home screen, or both. Enjoy a fresh look and express your style easily!</p>
